data.description: Discover a world of opportunity with this As-Is gem! This house boasts excellent bones and finishes, laminate flooring throughout (including both of the spacious bedrooms), a nice open-concept floorplan and large windows allowing in tons of natural light.The front walkway received a makeover just a few years ago with new stones to welcome you home in style. And to ensure you can lookforward to comfy-cozy winters, the seller had a brand-new boiler installed in November 2022.   With a price that will make your wallet smile, this home is ready for you to transform it into your dream home! Schedule your showing today!
